column142:
Includes deposits earmarked to SBPE: 6.17% p.a. + TR if Selic target is more than 8.5% p.a. or 70% of Selic target + TR if Selic target is equal or less than 8.5% p.a;
Time deposits and additional requirements on demand deposits, time deposits and savings deposits: Selic;
Savings deposits not invested in rural or habitational credit: 80% (6.17% p.a. + TR if Selic target is more than 8.5% p.a. or 70% of Selic target + TR if Selic target is equal or less than 8.5% p.a. ).
As of August 2016, it includes resources from Agribusiness Credit Bonds or LCA not invested in rural credit (same remuneration of deposits earmarked to SPPE).
